    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through high-revving individual throttle bodies. It remains mechanically robust with a recently serviced VANOS system and reinforced rear subframe mounts to address chassis fatigue. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Riding on a refreshed suspension with poly bushings and Bilstein dampers, the turn-in remains sharp. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its driver-focused history, the drivetrain and cooling system have been meticulously maintained for peak performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
