      "description": "This vehicle represents the perfect balance of luxury and reliability. The exterior is finished in a deep obsidian metallic that still holds a high-gloss luster, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the charcoal leather upholstery has been meticulously maintained, showing minimal bolster wear and no cracks. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium surround-sound system, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust; it has a documented service history, including a recent fluid flush and a fresh set of high-performance all-season tires. The engine pulls smoothly and the transmission shifts are crisp and seamless. This is a turn-key vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for many more miles of dependable service.",
      "price": 34500.0,
