      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been treated with a lot of love, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for many more adventures with you! It drives beautifully and looks great, making it the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend trips. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
